<ansi fg="yellow-bold">balance</ansi> - Check combat balance status

<ansi fg="cyan">Usage:</ansi>
  balance

<ansi fg="cyan">Description:</ansi>
  Shows your current balance status in twitch combat. Displays whether
  you are balanced and ready to act, or how much time remains until
  you regain balance.

  Also shows your weapon recovery time and base wait information.

<ansi fg="cyan">Examples:</ansi>
  balance     - Check your current balance status

<ansi fg="cyan">Note:</ansi>
  This command is only available when twitch combat is active.
  In round-based combat, attacks happen automatically each round.

<ansi fg="yellow">See Also:</ansi> attack, target, cleartarget, combatinfo